# Full API base URL including API version segment (same shape as gt-app local/remote base + version).
# Example: http://giftabulatornow.test/v2.1
VITE_API_BASE_URL=

# Optional dev-only: avoid browser CORS by proxying through Vite.
# 1) Set proxy target to your PHP host (no path): e.g. http://giftabulatornow.test
# 2) Set API base to the proxy prefix (see vite.config.ts):
# VITE_DEV_PROXY_TARGET=http://giftabulatornow.test
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=/__gt_api
